lass="t m15d x92 h15 y5fc ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">delayeth His coming&quot;? What will this attitude lead </div><div class="t m454 x92 h15 ye1c ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">him to do ? Matt. 24 : 48, 49. </div><div class="t m1d0 x14 h15 y616 ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">6. </div><div class="t m313 x36 h15 y616 ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">How will such servants be surprised? What will </div><div class="t maf2 x92 h15 y41e ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">be their portion ? How will their disappointment af-, </div><div class="t mb15 x92 h15 y6a ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">feet them? Verses 50, 51. Note 3. </div><div class="t m767 xa h4 y600 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">THE PARABLE OF THE VIRGINS </div><div class="t m1d2 x14 h15 y356 ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">7. </div><div class="t m260 x28 h15 y356 ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">To what did Jesus liken the kingdom of heaven ? </div><div class="t m26b x92 h15 y72e ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Matt. 25: 1. </div><div class="t m1d5 x14 h15 y36b ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">8. </div><div class="t m27c x28 h15 y36b ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">What is said of these virgins ? Verse 2. </div><div class="t m127 x14 h15 y61a ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">9. </div><div class="t m73b x28 h15 y1e1 ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">In what respect were five of them foolish? How </div><div class="t m2ef x92 h15 y392 ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">did the other five virgins manifest wisdom? Verses </div><div class="t mb36 x92 h15 y2ca ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">3, 4. </div><div class="t me4 x71 h15 y480 ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">10. </div><div class="t m616 x36 h15 y480 ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">After the ten virgins took their lamps and went </div><div class="t m9d x92 h15 y256 ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">forth to meet the bridegroom, what took place? Be-</div><div class="t mae x92 h15 y953 ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">cause the bridegroom tarried, what did the virgins do? </div><div class="t m194b x92 h15 y2037 ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Verse 5. Note 4. </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000